sequenceDiagram
    participant App as 应用主线程
    participant AMS as AMS / ActiveServices
    participant Handler as AMS Handler
    participant AnrHelper as AnrHelper

    Note over AMS: === 埋弹阶段 ===
    AMS->>App: scheduleCreateService() / scheduleReceiver()
    AMS->>Handler: sendMessageDelayed(TIMEOUT_MSG, 超时阈值)
    Note over Handler: 定时炸弹已设置

    alt 正常完成（拆弹）
        App->>AMS: serviceDoneExecuting() / finishReceiver()
        AMS->>Handler: removeMessages(TIMEOUT_MSG)
        Note over Handler: 定时炸弹已拆除
    else 超时（爆炸）
        Handler->>Handler: handleMessage(TIMEOUT_MSG)
        Handler->>AnrHelper: appNotResponding()
        Note over AnrHelper: === ANR 处理阶段 ===
        AnrHelper->>AnrHelper: 收集 CPU 信息
        AnrHelper->>App: 发送 SIGQUIT 信号
        App->>App: ART dump 所有线程堆栈
        App-->>AnrHelper: traces.txt 写入完成
        AnrHelper->>AnrHelper: 写入 EventLog / DropBox
        alt 前台进程
            AnrHelper->>App: 弹出 ANR 对话框
        else 后台进程
            AnrHelper->>App: 静默 kill 进程
        end
    end
